<section_header_level_1><loc_219><loc_266><loc_288><loc_272>WITNESSETH:  That</section_header_level_1>
<text><loc_78><loc_281><loc_428><loc_312>WHEREAS,  by virtue  of the Decision  dated December 01, 2021 of the Honorable supreme  court in G.R.  No. 235316 entitled  "Municipality  of Makati  vs. Municipality of Tagui8", confirmed that ten  (10) barangays  in Parcels 3 & 4 of Psu-2031  are  part  of the territory oJ Taguig City.</text>
<text><loc_78><loc_320><loc_387><loc_336>wHEREAS, several  public  schools  located within the said area were previously administered  by DEPED  Makati Division.</text>
<text><loc_78><loc_343><loc_407><loc_366>WHEREAs,  Makati  City maintains that the Supreme Court decision does not vest ownership of the school land, building,  facilities  and equipment in favor  of Tagui8 but only provides  that said schools  are within  the territorial  iurisdiction  of Taguig City'</text>
<text><loc_79><loc_375><loc_440><loc_398>WHEREAS, Taguig City on the other hand asserts that by virtue of the above-mentioned supreme court decision and other applicable  laws,  ownership  of the sch al land, buildine,  andafacilities, and  equipment belong to TaguiS City and/or the DEPED.</text>
